lyrics:

chorus
tween them almosthad’ems and broken bones
the dream of a buckle ill never put on

and id do it all again even though we both know

see cody johnson liveget tickets as low as 15you might also likechorus

but somehow the highs outweigh the lows

instrumental bridge
